      • parseEasing

        public static TweenEquation parseEasing(java.lang.String easingName)
        Takes an easing name and gives you the corresponding TweenEquation. You probably won't need this, but tools will love that.
        参数:
        easingName - The name of an easing, like "Quad.INOUT".
        返回:
        The parsed equation, or null if there is no match.
